elements.name: Launch the ACS application and login the application ACS_GMR_Import

steps.name: I login with "ACS USER" user given in "Login" sheet ACS_GMR_Import

elements.name: create a direct shipment ACS_GMR_Import single BOE single VT.

steps.name: To verify whether the user is able to Approve the Airline DO request from Kale Airline account
To verify whether the user is able to do Weight verification of Consol Shipment
To verify whether the user is able to do Consol DO and assign the shipment as self for Consol Shipment
To verify whether the user is able to do Consol DO and assign the shipment to another CB
To verify whether the user is able to do BoE for Direct/Consol Shipment
To verify whether the user is able to do Pick Order for Direct/Consol Shipment
To verify whether the user is able to do OOC for Direct/Consol Shipment
To verify whether the user is able to BoE ASI and View the ACS Receipt for Direct/Consol Shipment
To check if user can create TSP for Direct/Consol shipment as self assign.
To check if user is able to assign the shipment to Consignee to create TSP for Direct/Consol shipment
To check if user is able to create single VT for single BoE  from TSP pop up
To check if user is able to create single VT for single BoE  from  Shipment list page
To verify whether user is able to generate the token on click of Generate Token button
To verify whether the user is able to Revoke and Send ADO again from Airlines login
To verify whether the user is able to view Reject icon when the CTO rejects the Wt.Verification and again the user is able to resubmit the Wt.Verification.
To verify whether the user is able to do BoE and view complete icon when CTO Approves BoE for Direct/Consol Shipment with Manual Type
To verify whether the user is able to take print of Pick Order for Direct/Consol Shipment
To verify whether the user is able to view Complete icon for Dock In/Dock Out on Track and Trace screen when the CTO perform Dock In/Dock Out activity.
To verify whether the user is able to View Partial Complete icon for Dock In/Dock Out on Track and Trace screen when the CTO perform Dock In/Dock Out activity for 1 VT out of 2 VT.
To verify whether user is able to Cancel the token on click of Cancel Token Button from VCT screen
To check whether the system displays proper status for ARR,RCF,NFD,ADO,DI,Consol DO, BoE, RFE,FFE,OOC, TSP,VT,GD with proper date and timestamp.
To check when user clicks on AWB number and it should display its  details and correct status in its respective fields.
To verify whether user is able to View the Transaction Report From Sub-menu of Reports
To verify whether user is able to View the Dwell Time Report From Sub-menu of Reports
To verify whether user is able to View the Tonnage Report
To verify whether user is able to release and revoke DO in bulk.
